The angle formula_52 in these formulas is called the true anomaly of the point. The numerator formula_63 of these formulas is the semi-latus rectum of the ellipse, usually denoted formula_64. It is the distance from a focus of the ellipse to the ellipse itself, measured along a line perpendicular to the major axis.
